column5: Here is a pic of the great lures I won through the FoF  show review.  Thanks to Mr Mercer and TJ.  I will be using some of that plastic tomorrow while trying to catch some Lakers.

As did mine!!!  Only one problem , the gulp pack broke...peeee youuu!!!!!!!!! Nothing a good washing of wont help!  Big props out to Dave and TJ!!   Going to be using those sinking worms on some big old largemouths this year!   Darren
Yup, got mine today too.  What a nice surprise.  Great package  Thanks Dave and TJ, very much appreciated.  Joey
well that's just not right  you sure my name wasn't on it.. nice haul there for sure
Did you answer any questions for me Terry??? I don't seem to have a package in the mail box..
Hey cool, good for you Doug!
